Package: climateTR
Title: Temporal aggregation and Trend analysis of raster time series climate data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Francis Michael", "Msangi", , "francismich196@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3663-641X"))
Description: This package performs temporal aggregation of raster times series climate data including days, monthly, annual and seasonal, and performs trend analysis based on a parametric method(linear regression) and non-parametric method (Mann Kendall).
